<div class="col-md-8" style="color : #fff;margin-bottom: 20px;border-left: 5px solid #737373;padding-left: 30px;text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000">
	<h3>Beginner Level</h3>
    <h4 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;padding-bottom: 20px;color: #ddd">If you do not have any driving experience, we recommend 20 to 30 hours of practical, behind-the-wheel training. We will teach you essential driving concepts through guided participation.	</h4>
    <h3>Refresher Level</h3>
    <h4 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;padding-bottom: 20px;color: #ddd">If you wish to enhance your driving skills, take 10 to 15 hours of practical training. You will be exposed to different traffic and weather conditions, highway driving and other advanced road techniques.	</h4>
    <h3>Remedial Level</h3>
    <h4 style="padding-bottom: 20px;color: #ddd">If you have not driven a vehicle for a period of time, take our 5 to 7 hours driving courses which will help bring back confidence on your driving skills.</h4>
